    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bearstone Campsite 是一款第一人称恐怖游戏，讲述了一个迷失在露营地的角色的冒险故事。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maria、Paul 和 Nathan 本不该丢下你。他们以为没有你这个理智的人也能应付？太荒谬了。他们成功了吗？你的手机没有信号，而你的朋友可能正绝望地等你来救。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/73e1aa5a9623c3c94e0ee4387aa3863b.poster.avif?t=1760372764\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/73e1aa5a9623c3c94e0ee4387aa3863b.webm?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/73e1aa5a9623c3c94e0ee4387aa3863b.mp4?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>见证他们的经历。因为你离开了，他们才陷入困境。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你一直很谨慎。或者说……胆小？这次你会怎么做？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/6fc56a0db8df85ea27c1d1ac37a4b4d4.poster.avif?t=1760372764\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/6fc56a0db8df85ea27c1d1ac37a4b4d4.webm?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/6fc56a0db8df85ea27c1d1ac37a4b4d4.mp4?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>没人能救你！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你身后可能一直有人。这里没有管理人员。你的手机是否有信号，也未可知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/e9f319d3f529fc95be4c31fe33b51cbb.poster.avif?t=1760372764\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/e9f319d3f529fc95be4c31fe33b51cbb.webm?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/e9f319d3f529fc95be4c31fe33b51cbb.mp4?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备好迎接夜晚的寂静</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须变得强大，才能在这场冒险中生存——从森林深处，到幽暗的下水道，再到冰冷的工厂走廊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/1db5d21a2157bb182d4b7dab1e480480.poster.avif?t=1760372764\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/1db5d21a2157bb182d4b7dab1e480480.webm?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/1db5d21a2157bb182d4b7dab1e480480.mp4?t=1760372764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你必须保持安静！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祈祷 <strong>Manbear</strong> 和 <strong>Howler</strong> 听不到你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在找到朋友之前，你不能离开！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个危险的环境中独自行动，只会让你丧命。你必须谨慎、冷静，做好迎接恐惧的准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>祝你好运！</strong></p>",
